- "regions, like towering trees" refers to areas with significant health data;
- "witnessed a significant number of confirmed cases" means areas with a high number of total confirmed cases;
- "population exceeding 10,000 souls" means areas with a total population greater than 10,000;
- "vaccination rates" refers to the vaccination rate per 100,000 population.
